1
00:00:05.797 --> 00:00:08.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We never cared what we did as long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as it annoyed the grown-ups.</c.bg_transparent>

2
00:00:09.317 --> 00:00:12.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All inner deflector shield subsystems</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are showing equal intensity.</c.bg_transparent>

3
00:00:13.395 --> 00:00:17.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Power balance levels are reading normal.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was a champion window breaker.</c.bg_transparent>

4
00:00:18.194 --> 00:00:21.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>On a dark night</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a few rocks I was deadly.</c.bg_transparent>

5
00:00:21.913 --> 00:00:24.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um, which 'you' are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:25.711 --> 00:00:27.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

7
00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:29.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're being hailed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by an incoming freighter.</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:30.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:32.589 --> 00:00:36.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen. Welcome to DS9.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Major Kira Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:36.388 --> 00:00:38.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is the Kobheerian Freighter</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Rak-Miunis</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:38.508 --> 00:00:39.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>requesting permission to dock.</i></c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:40.672 --> 00:00:43.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Docking Port 6 is clear for approach.</c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:43.346 --> 00:00:45.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Thank you. We have a passenger on board</i></c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:45.945 --> 00:00:47.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>requiring medical assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:47.945 --> 00:00:49.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you tell us what's wrong</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your passenger?</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:49.864 --> 00:00:52.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>He says it's a condition</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>called Kalla-Nohra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

17
00:00:52.263 --> 00:00:54.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It's apparently chronic</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>but he doesn't have his medication.</i></c.bg_transparent>

18
00:00:55.623 --> 00:00:57.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beam him directly to our Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:00:57.262 --> 00:00:58.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll have our doctor standing by.</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:00:58.942 --> 00:01:01.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Thank you, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> Rak-Miunis</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> out.</i></c.bg_transparent>

21
00:01:01.860 --> 00:01:03.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:01:03.460 --> 00:01:05.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is Bashir. Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:07.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Kobheerian transport</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is about to beam a patient to you.</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:07.939 --> 00:01:10.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's suffering from something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>called Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:11.577 --> 00:01:13.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm not aware of it.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll check the computer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:14.896 --> 00:01:19.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I'd like to go down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Infirmary and meet that patient.</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:19.935 --> 00:01:20.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Why?</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:21.549 --> 00:01:25.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only cases of Kalla-Nohra I know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of were the result of a mining accident</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:25.613 --> 00:01:28.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at a Bajoran forced labor camp</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I helped liberate.</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:28.931 --> 00:01:32.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The survivors of Gallitep have always been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a symbol to us of strength and courage.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:33.911 --> 00:01:35.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By all means, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take as much time as you want.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:50.566 --> 00:01:52.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, Major. I'll be right with you.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:01:58.323 --> 00:01:59.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Kira to Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

34
00:01:59.563 --> 00:02:02.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I need security here on the double.</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:02:02.482 --> 00:02:03.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm on my way, Major.</i></c.bg_transparent>

36
00:04:00.887 --> 00:04:02.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the matter, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:04:02.566 --> 00:04:04.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your patient is a criminal.</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:04:08.764 --> 00:04:10.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:04:12.963 --> 00:04:14.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good afternoon.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:04:15.643 --> 00:04:17.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assume this is the problem.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:04:17.842 --> 00:04:19.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-MARRITZA: Problem?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Lock him up.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:04:19.641 --> 00:04:21.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is outrageous. On what charge?</c.bg_transparent>

43
00:04:21.681 --> 00:04:24.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Will somebody tell me what's going on?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This man needs medical care.</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:04:24.880 --> 00:04:27.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Then give it to him in his cell.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I haven't done anything.</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:04:28.387 --> 00:04:29.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why did you run?</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:04:29.478 --> 00:04:31.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm trying to get away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this Bajoran fanatic.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:04:32.317 --> 00:04:34.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The look of hate in her eyes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she'd like to kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:04:34.797 --> 00:04:37.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh? And why would that be?</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:04:37.276 --> 00:04:39.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's obvious. I'm a Cardassian.</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:04:39.435 --> 00:04:43.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not just any Cardassian.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's a war criminal.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:04:50.472 --> 00:04:53.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you're saying this man...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's his name?</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:04:53.191 --> 00:04:54.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza. Aamin Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:04:55.708 --> 00:04:57.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza's on the Bajorans' list</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:04:57.310 --> 00:04:59.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>for Cardassians wanted for war crimes?</c.bg_transparent>

55
00:04:59.430 --> 00:05:01.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not on any list</c.bg_transparent>

56
00:05:01.429 --> 00:05:03.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've seen, Commander,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I've got them all.</c.bg_transparent>

57
00:05:03.868 --> 00:05:05.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't care whether he's listed or not...</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:05:05.868 --> 00:05:06.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold on, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:05:07.187 --> 00:05:09.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza is traveling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on a Federation ship.</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:05:09.186 --> 00:05:12.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>He comes here for a medical emergency</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and we throw him into a security cell.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:05:12.546 --> 00:05:14.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I, for one, hope he's listed.</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:05:14.185 --> 00:05:16.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what I've done isn't exactly policy</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:05:17.184 --> 00:05:18.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and may not even be legal, but it's right.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:05:18.984 --> 00:05:20.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, Major, what do we charge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>him with?</c.bg_transparent>

65
00:05:20.583 --> 00:05:23.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm charging him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with having contracted Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>

66
00:05:23.782 --> 00:05:25.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you want to explain that to me?</c.bg_transparent>

67
00:05:25.261 --> 00:05:27.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only way he could have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>contracted that condition</c.bg_transparent>

68
00:05:27.581 --> 00:05:29.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>was to have served</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the Gallitep labor camp</c.bg_transparent>

69
00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:31.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>at the time of the mining accident.</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:05:31.539 --> 00:05:33.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, that makes him a war</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>criminal, just being there?</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:05:33.739 --> 00:05:37.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you'd been there 12 years ago</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:05:37.538 --> 00:05:41.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>when we liberated that camp</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you'd seen the things I saw</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:05:41.816 --> 00:05:45.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>all those Bajoran bodies,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>starved, brutalized...</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:05:46.215 --> 00:05:48.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know what Cardassian policy was?</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:05:48.215 --> 00:05:49.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm not even talking about the murder.</c.bg_transparent>

76
00:05:49.934 --> 00:05:51.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Murder was just the end</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the fun for them.</c.bg_transparent>

77
00:05:51.413 --> 00:05:52.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>First came the humiliation.</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:05:53.253 --> 00:05:55.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mothers raped in front of their children,</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:05:55.812 --> 00:05:58.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>husbands beaten until their wives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>couldn't recognize them,</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:05:58.811 --> 00:06:01.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>old people buried alive,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because they couldn't work anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:06:10.648 --> 00:06:12.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I'll have a talk with our guest.</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:06:13.247 --> 00:06:14.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll come with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:06:15.207 --> 00:06:16.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It'd be better if I spoke to him alone.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:06:29.277 --> 00:06:29.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you feel?</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:06:30.482 --> 00:06:31.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Better, thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:06:33.813 --> 00:06:35.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Benjamin Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in charge of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:38.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, finally. The Federation to the rescue.</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:06:39.439 --> 00:06:41.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you going to get me out of here?</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:06:41.318 --> 00:06:42.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope so.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:06:43.358 --> 00:06:46.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, how did you contract</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kalla-Nohra Syndrome?</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:06:46.917 --> 00:06:49.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have Pottrik Syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:06:50.196 --> 00:06:51.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The freighter captain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>said it was Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:06:52.475 --> 00:06:53.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A very similar condition.</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:06:54.115 --> 00:06:56.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take the same medication,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a matter of fact.</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:06:56.594 --> 00:06:58.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then you didn't serve</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the Gallitep labor camp?</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:06:59.394 --> 00:07:00.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Labor camp? ( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:07:01.113 --> 00:07:06.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. I've never been to Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was a military file clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:07:07.551 --> 00:07:12.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I reside now on Kora II</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where I boarded a freighter</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:07:12.510 --> 00:07:14.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which, unfortunately for me, came here.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:15.429 --> 00:07:17.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, Commander,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you have no more questions</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:17.468 --> 00:07:18.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like to be on my way.</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:07:18.668 --> 00:07:19.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I still drunk</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:20.747 --> 00:07:24.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or am I in jail with a Cardassian?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:24.746 --> 00:07:25.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:25.826 --> 00:07:28.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not keeping me in here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with one of those.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:29.665 --> 00:07:30.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:31.704 --> 00:07:32.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:32.783 --> 00:07:35.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I put myself in your hands, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:45.339 --> 00:07:46.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me get this straight.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:46.579 --> 00:07:48.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying Marritza</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>does have Kalla-Nohra?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:48.419 --> 00:07:50.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: There's no doubt about it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He has all the symptoms.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:50.898 --> 00:07:53.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And when I ran a lower pulmonary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>bio-probe, he read positive.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:53.817 --> 00:07:55.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you're sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he doesn't have Pottrik Syndrome?</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:55.936 --> 00:07:59.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, absolutely. If he had Pottrik's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the bio-probe would have been negative.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:00.375 --> 00:08:02.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then he was at the Gallitep labor camp.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:03.545 --> 00:08:03.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Definitely.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:04.134 --> 00:08:06.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've cross-checked all Bajoran</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Federation medical records</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:06.733 --> 00:08:09.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there's simply no other way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he could have gotten this condition.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:09.413 --> 00:08:10.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Kira to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:10.612 --> 00:08:11.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:11.692 --> 00:08:14.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander, there's an incoming</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>transmission for you from Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:14.771 --> 00:08:15.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It's the Minister of State.</i></c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:16.250 --> 00:08:18.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you. If you'll excuse me, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:23.608 --> 00:08:25.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minister Kaval. Good day, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:25.488 --> 00:08:27.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>And to you, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I trust you're in good health.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:28.167 --> 00:08:29.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Things are going well on the station?</i></c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:29.686 --> 00:08:30.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite well, thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:30.726 --> 00:08:33.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>That's wonderful.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm told you've performed</i></c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:33.446 --> 00:08:35.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>a special service for Bajor today.</i></c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:35.804 --> 00:08:36.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Congratulations to you.</i></c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:37.204 --> 00:08:38.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't quite follow.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:39.724 --> 00:08:41.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You're not holding</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a certain Cardassian for us?</i></c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:42.203 --> 00:08:45.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are holding a Cardassian temporarily.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:45.825 --> 00:08:47.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>By temporarily, you mean,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>until you are satisfied</i></c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:48.959 --> 00:08:50.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that a verified identification</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>has been made.</i></c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:53.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Minister, I'm not sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have the grounds to hold him that long.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:53.959 --> 00:08:57.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I fully understand your concerns,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander but since our Major Kira</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:57.678 --> 00:09:01.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>has accepted responsibility in this matter</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the burden is off your shoulders.</i></c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:01.117 --> 00:09:02.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't agree.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:02.116 --> 00:09:07.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander if this Marritza was at Gallitep</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>we want him, and we will have him.</i></c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:07.795 --> 00:09:08.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Is that clear?</i></c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:09.674 --> 00:09:10.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:11.194 --> 00:09:12.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Good.</i></c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:13.113 --> 00:09:16.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll chat again soon.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Good day, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:36.866 --> 00:09:38.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: May I join you?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:38.626 --> 00:09:42.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I was just about to pay a visit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to our friend, Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:42.624 --> 00:09:44.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's what I want to talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to you about, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:45.237 --> 00:09:47.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like Odo to handle this investigation.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:48.823 --> 00:09:49.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:49.822 --> 00:09:51.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's our Chief of Security.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:53.619 --> 00:09:56.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Minister Kaval put me in charge.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Minister Kaval doesn't run this station.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:57.260 --> 00:10:00.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the Federation has no right</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>telling us how to deal with our criminals.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:00.419 --> 00:10:02.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it turns out that he is a criminal</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:02.338 --> 00:10:04.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then he'll be yours,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you're welcome to him.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:04.897 --> 00:10:07.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until then,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he's just a traveler under suspicion.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:08.697 --> 00:10:09.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:13.135 --> 00:10:16.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think this is all some personal</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>vendetta on my part, don't you?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:16.614 --> 00:10:19.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you're too close</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be objective, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:19.213 --> 00:10:20.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right. I'm not objective.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:22.492 --> 00:10:27.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'm your First Officer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I give you my word</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:27.171 --> 00:10:29.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will conduct myself accordingly.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:34.169 --> 00:10:39.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You once said we were friends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you now, as a friend,</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:39.968 --> 00:10:44.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>please, let me conduct this investigation.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:45.166 --> 00:10:46.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I owe it to them.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:48.125 --> 00:10:50.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You mean the victims.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:52.883 --> 00:10:55.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ones who moved too slowly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and never moved again.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:58.202 --> 00:11:02.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking for all the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who can't ask.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:05.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let a Bajoran do this.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:14.157 --> 00:11:15.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sisko to Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:15.477 --> 00:11:16.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:17.356 --> 00:11:22.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Constable, Major Kira will be in charge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Marritza investigation.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:24.114 --> 00:11:25.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>I understand.</i></c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:28.832 --> 00:11:29.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:43.291 --> 00:11:43.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Constable.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:44.683 --> 00:11:45.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's about time you let me out.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:11:45.867 --> 00:11:49.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to stay out of trouble</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a day or two, will you?</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:11:49.187 --> 00:11:50.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do my best.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:51.186 --> 00:11:55.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, and Odo, let me know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you hang the Cardassian.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:59.863 --> 00:12:02.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've begun a background check on Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:02.302 --> 00:12:04.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So far he is what he says he is.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:04.861 --> 00:12:08.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He boarded that Kobheerian</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>freighter at Kora II</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:08.341 --> 00:12:09.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>where he's worked as an instructor</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:09.621 --> 00:12:12.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at a military academy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the past five years.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:13.139 --> 00:12:14.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep looking.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:14.299 --> 00:12:16.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry, Major, I intend to.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:17.698 --> 00:12:19.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be with the prisoner if you need me.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:25.175 --> 00:12:27.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MARRITZA: My compliments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on your replicators, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:27.894 --> 00:12:32.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>sem'hal </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>stew</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could use a little </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>yamoksauce.</i></c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:32.893 --> 00:12:35.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm glad you're enjoying it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I doubt that, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:35.612 --> 00:12:37.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt it very much.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:38.292 --> 00:12:40.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope it won't disturb your dinner</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if I ask you a few questions.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:41.610 --> 00:12:43.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-If I refuse to answer?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll ask them anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:44.450 --> 00:12:45.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:46.889 --> 00:12:48.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is my job.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:48.649 --> 00:12:51.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Persecuting Cardassians goes far beyond</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your job, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:51.568 --> 00:12:52.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your passion.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:56.127 --> 00:12:58.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You claim you were never at Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:59.649 --> 00:13:00.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MARITZZA: I missed that honor.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:01.725 --> 00:13:04.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And that your illness is not Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Again, true.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:05.445 --> 00:13:06.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Again, false.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:06.963 --> 00:13:09.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our doctor confirmed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you do have Kalla-Nohra</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:09.362 --> 00:13:11.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which means you were at Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:13:13.281 --> 00:13:14.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If your lies are going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be this transparent</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:17.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it's going to be a very</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>short interrogation.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:19.396 --> 00:13:21.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, in that case, I'll try to make</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my lies more opaque.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:25.517 --> 00:13:27.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was your rank at Gallitep?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What were your duties?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:28.768 --> 00:13:29.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want to know.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:29.516 --> 00:13:32.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Just answer the question.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You'll be disappointed.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:34.315 --> 00:13:35.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll risk it.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:37.914 --> 00:13:42.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had the distinction of serving</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the exalted position of filing clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:42.993 --> 00:13:44.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Filing clerk?</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:44.712 --> 00:13:46.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you you'd be disappointed.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:47.431 --> 00:13:50.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, I would have preferred</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to avoid military service altogether</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:50.430 --> 00:13:54.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I had the good fortune to be posted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the records office at Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:54.149 --> 00:13:55.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I turned out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be an exemplary file clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:56.388 --> 00:13:57.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In 14 units of service</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:57.948 --> 00:14:01.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never misplaced or lost a record.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I received numerous commendations.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:02.272 --> 00:14:04.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gul Darhe'el, himself,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>called my computer filing system,</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:04.706 --> 00:14:07.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"a masterpiece of meticulous exactitude."</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:08.305 --> 00:14:10.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, there you are. My secret's out.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:11.644 --> 00:14:12.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My crimes laid bare.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:13.584 --> 00:14:14.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await execution.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:16.231 --> 00:14:17.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope we don't keep you waiting long.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:23.940 --> 00:14:25.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I never heard of a filing clerk</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:25.819 --> 00:14:28.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>becoming an instructor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at a military academy.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:29.179 --> 00:14:30.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Until now.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What did you teach?</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:30.938 --> 00:14:33.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Believe it or not, filing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can verify that.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:34.180 --> 00:14:34.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be my guest.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:36.416 --> 00:14:37.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I still think you're a liar.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:40.295 --> 00:14:42.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So much for our search</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the truth. Now we trade insults.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:44.814 --> 00:14:46.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You admit you worked under Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:47.693 --> 00:14:48.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all did.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:48.893 --> 00:14:50.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it, then, you witnessed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the atrocities.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:51.212 --> 00:14:52.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Atrocities?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:53.212 --> 00:14:54.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What atrocities?</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:57.690 --> 00:15:00.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I vaguely recall hearing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a scream from time to time.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:15:02.448 --> 00:15:03.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Atrocities? No.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:15:04.208 --> 00:15:09.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe you knew nothing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the murders, the tortures?</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:10.126 --> 00:15:12.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You never saw the bodies?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course I saw bodies.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:12.486 --> 00:15:14.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>People died all the time at Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:14.325 --> 00:15:17.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mining accidents, illnesses,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>feuds among the workers.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:19.369 --> 00:15:21.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You're saying Bajorans killed each other?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-At times.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:22.842 --> 00:15:25.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Over food, a blanket, a woman.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:26.601 --> 00:15:29.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The conditions were harsh.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It was a labor camp, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:30.840 --> 00:15:33.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I helped liberate that camp.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I saw the bodies.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:34.159 --> 00:15:35.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know how they died.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:35.719 --> 00:15:37.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You saw what we wanted you to see.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:38.278 --> 00:15:41.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who do you think started the rumors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about brutality at Gallitep?</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:41.636 --> 00:15:43.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was Gul Darhe'el himself.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:43.476 --> 00:15:46.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, there was a leader.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Brilliant, extraordinary man.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:46.715 --> 00:15:49.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He knew that to rule by fear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was to rule completely.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:49.594 --> 00:15:53.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why bother with actual mass murders</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when just the reports of such incidents</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:54.753 --> 00:15:56.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>would have the same effect?</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:15:57.112 --> 00:15:57.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which was?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:15:58.152 --> 00:15:59.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know as well as I do, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:15:59.871 --> 00:16:02.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To keep you Bajorans thinking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of yourselves as victims.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:02.271 --> 00:16:03.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To keep you afraid and helpless.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:05.590 --> 00:16:09.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Turns out we weren't so helpless.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We did get rid of you.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:10.908 --> 00:16:16.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leaving was a political decision, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've enjoyed reminiscing with you.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:16.626 --> 00:16:19.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I think it's time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you let me out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:19.185 --> 00:16:20.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:21.505 --> 00:16:23.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no, no, no, no, of course not.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:23.224 --> 00:16:25.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, you see, you're the one</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who's lying now, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:25.584 --> 00:16:28.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not the truth you're interested in.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>All you want is vengeance.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:42.378 --> 00:16:46.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander, I was led to believe</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the Federation guarantees</i></c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:46.978 --> 00:16:48.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>the safe and unrestricted passage</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of all travelers</i></c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:48.816 --> 00:16:50.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>visiting your station.</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:50.896 --> 00:16:52.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's correct.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Then, how do you explain</i></c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:52.935 --> 00:16:55.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>the detention of a Cardassian citizen?</i></c.bg_transparent>

270
00:16:55.375 --> 00:16:57.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza came here seeking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>medical attention.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:58.254 --> 00:16:59.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, he's under our doctor's care.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:17:00.373 --> 00:17:02.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All we're trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to do is to verify his identity.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:17:03.173 --> 00:17:05.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A simple matter, if you'll give us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some assistance.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:17:05.932 --> 00:17:09.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I assure you, Commander,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>you don't need our assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>

275
00:17:09.650 --> 00:17:14.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>If this patient says his name is Marritza</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>then that's who he is.</i></c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:15.688 --> 00:17:17.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I hope you're not suggesting</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>you don't trust him</i></c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:17.808 --> 00:17:19.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>simply because he's Cardassian.</i></c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:19.847 --> 00:17:21.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because he's already lied</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:21.927 --> 00:17:23.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>about being at Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:23.646 --> 00:17:25.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Is that what you're charging</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>him with, Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:26.886 --> 00:17:27.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Lying?</i></c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:28.245 --> 00:17:30.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So far, we haven't charged him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with anything.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:17:30.564 --> 00:17:31.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Then let him go.</i></c.bg_transparent>

284
00:17:31.924 --> 00:17:33.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like nothing better.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:17:33.803 --> 00:17:35.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But first, I need to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who it is I'm letting go.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:17:37.522 --> 00:17:41.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I do appreciate the awkwardness</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of your position here, Commander.</i></c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:47.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This Bajoran obsession</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>with alleged Cardassian improprieties</i></c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:48.199 --> 00:17:52.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>during the occupation</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>is really quite distasteful.</i></c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:52.437 --> 00:17:55.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose, if you're a Bajoran,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so was the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:55.436 --> 00:17:58.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I might remind you</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>that neither one</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>of us is Bajoran</i></c.bg_transparent>

291
00:18:00.235 --> 00:18:01.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and I would hate their bitterness</i></c.bg_transparent>

292
00:18:02.349 --> 00:18:05.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>to cause conflict between</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Cardassia and the Federation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:06.354 --> 00:18:09.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope to avoid that, too with your help.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:09.832 --> 00:18:15.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You don't need my help to safeguard</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>one Cardassian citizen on your station.</i></c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:16.190 --> 00:18:19.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>If any of these Bajoran hate mongers</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>get their hands on him</i></c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:20.869 --> 00:18:23.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll hold you personally responsible.</i></c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:40.903 --> 00:18:41.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you looking for?</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:44.262 --> 00:18:45.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Answers.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:18:46.102 --> 00:18:47.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Found any yet?</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:18:49.860 --> 00:18:52.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza says I don't care</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:52.899 --> 00:18:57.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That all I want is vengeance.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you worried that maybe he's right?</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:19:00.138 --> 00:19:02.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I want is to see him punished.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:19:05.256 --> 00:19:07.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if he is just a file clerk?</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:19:07.495 --> 00:19:10.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's just it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want him to be just a file clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:19:10.494 --> 00:19:14.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want him to be...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know... something worse.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:19:17.212 --> 00:19:18.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want him to be guilty.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:19.531 --> 00:19:22.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as I'm concerned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if he was at Gallitep, he is guilty.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:22.611 --> 00:19:23.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're all guilty.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:25.210 --> 00:19:29.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His punishment will let Bajor feel some...</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:31.208 --> 00:19:32.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Satisfaction.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:35.246 --> 00:19:38.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds like you're trying too hard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to believe what you're saying</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:40.245 --> 00:19:42.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You already know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you punish him without reason</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:42.725 --> 00:19:46.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it won't mean anything.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And you already know vengeance...</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:47.643 --> 00:19:48.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't enough.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:20:06.957 --> 00:20:09.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reroute the signal enhancement module</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the main sensor array.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:20:10.317 --> 00:20:11.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:20:15.755 --> 00:20:16.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How's it look?</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:20:17.354 --> 00:20:20.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just give me a second.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll run a diagnostic.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:20:22.913 --> 00:20:26.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've checked with the Bajoran Archives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and they do have a Marritza on record</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:26.632 --> 00:20:28.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as being a filing clerk at Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:28.671 --> 00:20:31.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've also checked with the military</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>academy on Kora II.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:31.670 --> 00:20:34.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza has been teaching filing there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just as he claims.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:34.869 --> 00:20:36.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'BRIEN: All set, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:36.349 --> 00:20:38.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, how many images were sent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the Bajoran archives?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:39.267 --> 00:20:40.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only one.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:40.147 --> 00:20:41.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the only picture</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they could find of Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:41.587 --> 00:20:42.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that had Marritza in it.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:42.787 --> 00:20:45.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Cardassians destroyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>almost all records of the occupation.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:45.666 --> 00:20:47.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The image enhancement</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and transformation functions</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:47.705 --> 00:20:49.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>are patched directly into your console.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:50.384 --> 00:20:53.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, what if this image confirms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Marritza was a file clerk?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:54.263 --> 00:20:55.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you expect us to do then?</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:57.102 --> 00:21:00.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I suppose you'll let him go.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm glad we understand each other.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:21:00.502 --> 00:21:02.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-DAX: I've got it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:21:04.207 --> 00:21:05.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Which one is Marritza?</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:21:05.140 --> 00:21:07.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Let's see... according to the caption</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:21:07.220 --> 00:21:09.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he's the one in the background</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the far right.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:21:09.898 --> 00:21:10.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isolate and magnify.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:14.697 --> 00:21:16.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have to do better than that.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:17.972 --> 00:21:18.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:21:18.216 --> 00:21:19.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm running an image</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>enhancement sequence.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:21:24.894 --> 00:21:25.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not him.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:21:26.293 --> 00:21:28.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're looking at the right man?</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:29.172 --> 00:21:31.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Background, far right, Aamin Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:21:32.491 --> 00:21:33.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It can't be.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:21:34.451 --> 00:21:36.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If that's Marritza,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then who are we holding here?</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:21:40.810 --> 00:21:44.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant, isolate the Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the foreground.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:21:46.327 --> 00:21:49.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The one in profile on the left</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what can you give us?</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:21:59.446 --> 00:22:00.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's him. That's Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:22:01.838 --> 00:22:03.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Not according to the caption.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:22:04.322 --> 00:22:06.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to this, it's Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:22:13.359 --> 00:22:14.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me guess.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:22:14.839 --> 00:22:16.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've come back to learn the secret</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of my filing system.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:22:17.638 --> 00:22:19.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know all your secrets now.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:22:19.677 --> 00:22:21.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is that so?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What did you do?</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:22:21.917 --> 00:22:24.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you kill the real Marritza</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so you could take his place?</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:22:25.636 --> 00:22:30.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you'll pay for that death</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and all the others you're responsible for.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:22:30.914 --> 00:22:32.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I don't think I could pay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for all of them, Major</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:22:33.343 --> 00:22:35.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>there were so many</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you can only execute me once.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:22:36.753 --> 00:22:38.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's my only regret.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:22:38.831 --> 00:22:43.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But... I'll settle for knowing that Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will finally have the satisfaction</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:22:43.750 --> 00:22:45.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of punishing the Butcher of Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:22:47.469 --> 00:22:50.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Did you figure this out all by yourself?</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:22:51.282 --> 00:22:53.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or did you have help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from your Federation masters?</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:22:54.307 --> 00:22:57.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll let you wonder about that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll keep you occupied</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:22:57.906 --> 00:22:59.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>while we're waiting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the provisional government</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:22:59.466 --> 00:23:01.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to prepare your war crimes tribunal.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:23:01.465 --> 00:23:02.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>War crimes?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:23:03.544 --> 00:23:06.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How could there be war crimes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when there hasn't been a war?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:23:06.624 --> 00:23:10.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can understand your wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that there had been a war.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:23:10.902 --> 00:23:12.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your need to indulge some pathetic fantasy</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:23:13.220 --> 00:23:15.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about brave Bajoran soldiers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>marching to honorable defeat.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:23:15.980 --> 00:23:19.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But, in fact, Major</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you and I know there was no war, no glory.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:23:19.620 --> 00:23:20.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor didn't resist.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:23:22.459 --> 00:23:23.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It surrendered.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:23:24.538 --> 00:23:26.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Bajorans were a peaceful</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>people before you came.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:23:26.577 --> 00:23:28.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We offered no threat to you.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:23:28.974 --> 00:23:30.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We could never understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why you had to be so brutal.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:23:30.617 --> 00:23:33.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we can't have that, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want no more secrets between us.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:23:33.655 --> 00:23:35.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anything you don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll explain to you.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:23:35.615 --> 00:23:37.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, but I think I've heard enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your lies.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:23:37.654 --> 00:23:38.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What lies?</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:23:38.694 --> 00:23:40.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean my failure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to divulge my true identity?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:23:40.853 --> 00:23:42.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Believe me, Major I yearned to tell you</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:23:42.933 --> 00:23:45.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I knew how much more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>satisfaction you would have</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:23:45.132 --> 00:23:47.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you found out for yourself.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And that was my only deception.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:23:47.651 --> 00:23:51.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza was a magnificent file clerk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I, Gul Darhe'el</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:23:51.889 --> 00:23:54.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you'll not think it immodest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of me to say so,</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:23:54.449 --> 00:23:56.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I was a magnificent leader.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:23:56.448 --> 00:23:58.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you never saw Gallitep at its height.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:23:59.882 --> 00:24:02.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For a labor camp it was the very model</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of order and efficiency.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:24:02.967 --> 00:24:03.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And why?</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:24:03.846 --> 00:24:06.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you have to look to the top. To me!</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:24:06.845 --> 00:24:09.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My word, my every glance was law</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:24:09.285 --> 00:24:11.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the verdict was always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the same, guilty.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:24:11.964 --> 00:24:13.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're insane.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:24:13.841 --> 00:24:14.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no, no, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:24:14.644 --> 00:24:19.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't dismiss me that easily.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I did what had to be done.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:24:19.201 --> 00:24:21.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My men understood that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and that's why they loved me.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:24:21.681 --> 00:24:24.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would order them to go out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and kill Bajoran scum</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:24:24.800 --> 00:24:26.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they'd do it, they'd murder them</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:24:26.800 --> 00:24:30.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they'd come back covered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in blood, but they felt clean.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:24:30.638 --> 00:24:32.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, why did they feel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that way, Major?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:24:33.376 --> 00:24:36.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Because they were clean.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You admit your atrocities.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:24:36.996 --> 00:24:38.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I admit everything.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:24:38.915 --> 00:24:43.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not? I was the best at what I did.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My accomplishments speak for themselves.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:24:43.194 --> 00:24:44.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you say the same?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:24:44.954 --> 00:24:47.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and that little Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>resistance cell</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:24:47.593 --> 00:24:50.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you belonged to.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>All you did was annoy Cardassians</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:24:50.512 --> 00:24:52.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>while I was out exterminating Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:24:52.432 --> 00:24:54.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make sure you tell that to the tribunal.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:24:54.511 --> 00:24:57.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, I will.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then they'll sentence you to death.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:24:57.390 --> 00:24:58.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let them.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:24:58.669 --> 00:25:00.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see, it doesn't change anything?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:25:00.949 --> 00:25:04.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill me, torture me it doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You've already lost, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:25:04.908 --> 00:25:06.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can never undo what I've accomplished.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:25:06.708 --> 00:25:08.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The dead will still be dead.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:25:11.546 --> 00:25:14.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What will you do now, Major?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Withhold my medicine?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:25:35.619 --> 00:25:37.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here. This will help.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:25:37.898 --> 00:25:40.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Maraltian </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>seev-ale</i></c.bg_transparent>

421
00:25:40.578 --> 00:25:42.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from Quark's private stock.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:25:46.415 --> 00:25:47.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Better?</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:25:49.574 --> 00:25:50.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, Odo</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:25:51.150 --> 00:25:54.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wonder how many others like Darhe'el</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are still out there...</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:25:54.853 --> 00:25:56.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Still free, unpunished.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:25:57.333 --> 00:25:58.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite a few, no doubt</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:25:59.772 --> 00:26:02.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but thanks to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there's one less out there now.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:26:03.331 --> 00:26:04.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should have heard him.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:26:05.610 --> 00:26:10.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He bragged about what happened at Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the torture, the murders, the humiliation.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:26:11.888 --> 00:26:13.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's proud about what he did to us.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:26:14.807 --> 00:26:17.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't you go to your quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and lie down for a while?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:26:17.966 --> 00:26:21.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll leave him alone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with his Cardassian pride.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:26:21.245 --> 00:26:22.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to lie down.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:26:23.164 --> 00:26:26.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, that's what he'd like another Bajoran</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hiding in a corner.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:26:27.723 --> 00:26:30.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's probably in there laughing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at me right now.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:26:30.122 --> 00:26:32.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He won't be laughing very long.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:26:33.161 --> 00:26:34.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hate him, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:26:35.169 --> 00:26:38.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hate his smirking,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>superior Cardassian face.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:26:39.599 --> 00:26:43.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I was fighting with the resistance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we used to lie awake at night</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:26:44.389 --> 00:26:46.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>plotting the assassination</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of men like Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:26:46.877 --> 00:26:48.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I have to stand there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and listen to him</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:26:48.317 --> 00:26:50.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>belittle the Shakaar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and everything it stood for.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:26:50.836 --> 00:26:54.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps you should avoid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>discussing your personal history</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:26:54.675 --> 00:26:55.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with a creature like that.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:26:56.115 --> 00:26:57.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:27:00.633 --> 00:27:02.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then how did he know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you were with the Shakaar?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:27:05.432 --> 00:27:08.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he was an important military leader.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:27:09.630 --> 00:27:10.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't explain it.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:27:12.699 --> 00:27:15.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he'd been in charge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of quelling Bajoran resistance</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:27:15.348 --> 00:27:19.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then he might have had your name on file</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he commanded a forced labor camp.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:27:20.627 --> 00:27:22.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Something's not right here.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:27:25.986 --> 00:27:27.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:27:27.386 --> 00:27:29.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To have another little chat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:27:35.303 --> 00:27:41.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, review all off-station requests</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for information regarding Major Kira Nerys</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:27:41.461 --> 00:27:43.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>within the last eight months.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:27:43.181 --> 00:27:44.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Working.</i></c.bg_transparent>

457
00:27:45.420 --> 00:27:48.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, back to see the Butcher.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Am I really so fascinating?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:27:49.989 --> 00:27:50.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you know I was with the Shakaar?</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:27:51.259 --> 00:27:52.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:27:52.937 --> 00:27:56.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This provisional government of yours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>certainly moves slowly.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:27:56.457 --> 00:27:58.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They should have dragged me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away in chains by now.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:27:58.496 --> 00:27:59.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Just answer the question!</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:27:59.616 --> 00:28:02.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, my, my, you are a strutting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>little egotist.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:28:03.735 --> 00:28:06.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You forget the brilliance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Marritza's filing system.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:28:06.813 --> 00:28:08.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He made sure that I was provided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with information</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:28:08.853 --> 00:28:10.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on all your little terrorist bands.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:28:10.972 --> 00:28:13.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I particularly enjoyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were the termination reports.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:28:13.931 --> 00:28:15.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:28:15.731 --> 00:28:18.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, life in a forced labor camp</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can be so isolating.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:28:18.890 --> 00:28:20.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At times, I felt that I alone</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:28:20.689 --> 00:28:23.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>bore the burden of cleansing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor of its rabble</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:28:23.209 --> 00:28:26.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but those reports reassured me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was not alone.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:28:27.168 --> 00:28:29.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm supposed to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you remembered my name</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:28:29.686 --> 00:28:31.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from some report you read years ago?</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:28:34.463 --> 00:28:36.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At the risk of bruising</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your vanity even further, Major</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:28:36.844 --> 00:28:39.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't remember you at all</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until I heard your name here.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:28:40.283 --> 00:28:41.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can see that disturbs you.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:28:41.723 --> 00:28:42.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hardly.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:28:42.883 --> 00:28:45.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, Major,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they will be coming for me soon</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:28:46.442 --> 00:28:47.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>so before we say good-bye</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:28:48.412 --> 00:28:50.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>there are a few little questions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should like to ask you.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:28:50.920 --> 00:28:54.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Your questions don't interest me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How can you be so sure?</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:28:55.519 --> 00:28:57.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or are you just afraid to hear them?</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:29:21.111 --> 00:29:22.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are they?</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:29:23.111 --> 00:29:26.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Survivors of Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They arrived early this morning.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:29:27.350 --> 00:29:29.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose they are waiting for justice.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:29:29.429 --> 00:29:30.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:29:31.228 --> 00:29:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Imagine living through that hellhole.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:29:33.827 --> 00:29:36.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pain... the sorrow...</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:29:38.146 --> 00:29:39.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think they like to gamble?</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:29:51.102 --> 00:29:53.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Doctor, I need your help.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:29:53.461 --> 00:29:56.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three months ago</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a request came from Kora II</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:29:56.301 --> 00:29:58.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for information concerning Kira Nerys.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:29:58.620 --> 00:30:00.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-To what purpose?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not sure.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:30:00.940 --> 00:30:04.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the name on the request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was Aamin Marritza.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:30:05.588 --> 00:30:08.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've established a subspace link</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Kora II</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:30:08.377 --> 00:30:10.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'd like you to access</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>his medical history there.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:30:10.657 --> 00:30:12.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dax to Odo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

499
00:30:12.296 --> 00:30:14.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Gul Dukat is responding</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to your subspace transmission.</i></c.bg_transparent>

500
00:30:15.455 --> 00:30:16.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could you route it to my office?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:30:16.614 --> 00:30:17.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aye, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

502
00:30:19.374 --> 00:30:25.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I do miss working with you, Odo.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I miss our games of Kalevian montar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

503
00:30:26.920 --> 00:30:29.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As I recall, Gul Dukat, we played one game</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:30:29.909 --> 00:30:30.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you cheated.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:30:30.490 --> 00:30:33.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:30:34.496 --> 00:30:38.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The same old Odo like a blunt instrument.</i></c.bg_transparent>

507
00:30:39.608 --> 00:30:41.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But now to your question.</i></c.bg_transparent>

508
00:30:41.447 --> 00:30:45.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I regret that I cannot give you</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>access to any of the files</i></c.bg_transparent>

509
00:30:45.486 --> 00:30:47.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pertaining to Gul Darhe'el.</i></c.bg_transparent>

510
00:30:48.126 --> 00:30:49.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But I assure you,</i></c.bg_transparent>

511
00:30:50.523 --> 00:30:52.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>the files would only tell you</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>what I am telling you.</i></c.bg_transparent>

512
00:30:53.837 --> 00:30:55.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Gul Darhe'el is dead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

513
00:30:56.522 --> 00:30:57.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not possible.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:30:58.202 --> 00:31:03.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I attended his funeral myself.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>As a matter of fact, he's buried</i></c.bg_transparent>

515
00:31:03.960 --> 00:31:07.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>under one of the largest</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>military monuments on Cardassia.</i></c.bg_transparent>

516
00:31:08.280 --> 00:31:10.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then who are we holding here?</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:31:10.518 --> 00:31:15.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Some innocent Cardassian citizen</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>as I explained to your Commander Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:31:16.477 --> 00:31:20.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-And we want him released.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That innocent citizen</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:31:20.476 --> 00:31:22.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has admitted he is Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:31:24.914 --> 00:31:27.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>What... are you saying?</i></c.bg_transparent>

521
00:31:28.273 --> 00:31:32.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He says his name is Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:31:32.952 --> 00:31:34.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Then he's lying.</i></c.bg_transparent>

523
00:31:34.351 --> 00:31:36.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if he is, it's the most foolish lie</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he could have invented.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:31:36.911 --> 00:31:39.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's likely to get him executed.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Why would anyone do such a thing?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:31:40.301 --> 00:31:40.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I don't know</i></c.bg_transparent>

526
00:31:41.749 --> 00:31:44.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but I tell you I attended</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Darhe'el's funeral.</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:31:44.988 --> 00:31:48.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're sure the man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you saw buried was Gul Darhe'el?</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:31:48.907 --> 00:31:51.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Half of Cardassia viewed his body.</i></c.bg_transparent>

529
00:31:51.786 --> 00:31:55.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saw a photograph of Gul Darhe'el</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>taken at the Gallitep labor camp.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:31:56.304 --> 00:31:58.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It certainly appears</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the man we're holding.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:31:58.704 --> 00:32:00.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-You're mistaken.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Am I?</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:32:00.943 --> 00:32:04.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is obviously some plot</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to embarrass the Cardassian Empire.</i></c.bg_transparent>

533
00:32:06.382 --> 00:32:07.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's possible.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:32:08.421 --> 00:32:11.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me access to your files</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and perhaps I can find some proof</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:32:12.208 --> 00:32:15.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to support your claim</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Gul Darhe'el is dead.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:32:15.499 --> 00:32:16.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:32:18.897 --> 00:32:23.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose I could grant you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>limited access to the files.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:32:26.136 --> 00:32:28.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think that's wise.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:32:33.293 --> 00:32:34.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was 12 when I started fighting</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:32:35.213 --> 00:32:37.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I've heard of some</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who were even younger than that.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:32:37.932 --> 00:32:39.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, yes, let's get to the real issue!</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:32:40.532 --> 00:32:42.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many Cardassians did you kill?</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:32:43.116 --> 00:32:44.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean personally.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:32:45.850 --> 00:32:48.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't keep count.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, I think you did.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:32:48.609 --> 00:32:52.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm sure your total wasn't limited</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to military personnel.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:32:52.128 --> 00:32:56.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, the most effective</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>terrorist weapon was random violence.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:32:56.247 --> 00:32:58.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't leave now, Major.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's just getting good.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:32:58.926 --> 00:33:01.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many Cardassian</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>civilians did you kill?</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:33:01.445 --> 00:33:04.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look! I regret a lot of what I had to do.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:33:04.125 --> 00:33:05.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MARITZZA: How convenient of you.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:33:05.364 --> 00:33:07.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had no choice!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We were fighting for survival.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:33:07.964 --> 00:33:10.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So were we. We had an Empire to protect.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:33:10.843 --> 00:33:15.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We needed your resources. Everything I did</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was for the greater glory of Cardassia!</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:33:16.360 --> 00:33:20.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if you spineless scum</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>had to be ground under so much the better.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:33:20.440 --> 00:33:23.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All that mattered was Cardassia.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I loved my homeland.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:33:23.159 --> 00:33:26.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's what justified my actions.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That's what gave me strength.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:33:26.998 --> 00:33:29.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing justifies genocide.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:33:29.796 --> 00:33:33.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you call genocide,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I call a day's work.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:33:36.475 --> 00:33:39.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, could I have a word with you?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:33:51.271 --> 00:33:53.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir and I have done some checking.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:33:54.430 --> 00:33:56.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know why yet</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:33:56.229 --> 00:33:59.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but the man in that cell</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted to be caught.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:34:12.983 --> 00:34:17.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This certificate of death</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was in the file sent to me by Gul Dukat.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:34:17.902 --> 00:34:20.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to this, Gul Darhe'el</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>died in his sleep six years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:34:21.614 --> 00:34:23.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Cause of death,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>massive coleibric hemorrhage."</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:34:23.940 --> 00:34:26.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I guarantee you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that is a forged document.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:34:27.220 --> 00:34:28.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's pretty clear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's going on here.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:34:28.739 --> 00:34:31.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Cardassians are trying to trick us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into letting him go.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:34:32.178 --> 00:34:34.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't put it past</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our friend Gul Dukat.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:34:35.179 --> 00:34:36.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nor would I, however...</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:34:36.416 --> 00:34:38.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The man in there confessed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he is Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:34:39.136 --> 00:34:42.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, the man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in there has Kalla-Nohra syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:34:43.375 --> 00:34:44.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course he does.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:34:44.694 --> 00:34:46.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to the evidence I've been sent</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:34:46.573 --> 00:34:49.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gul Darhe'el never contracted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that condition.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:34:49.693 --> 00:34:52.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>More evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from our trustworthy Gul Dukat.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:34:55.291 --> 00:34:56.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you got, Constable?</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:34:56.811 --> 00:34:59.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Darhe'el's progress reports from Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:34:59.169 --> 00:35:01.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>show that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when the mining accident occurred</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:35:01.729 --> 00:35:03.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he was back on Cardassia</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:35:03.329 --> 00:35:05.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>being awarded the Proficient</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Service Medallion.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:35:06.488 --> 00:35:08.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he wasn't at Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the day on the accident</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:35:09.407 --> 00:35:11.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then he couldn't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>contracted Kalla-Nohra.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:35:11.686 --> 00:35:12.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Correct.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:35:13.286 --> 00:35:15.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the man we're holding does have it.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:35:16.724 --> 00:35:18.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe I'm listening to this.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:35:18.644 --> 00:35:20.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid there's more, Major.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:35:21.365 --> 00:35:24.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I inquired about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this man's last two weeks on Kora II.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:35:24.643 --> 00:35:26.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He resigned his position</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the military academy</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:35:26.881 --> 00:35:28.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>put all his affairs in order</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:35:28.761 --> 00:35:30.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and even provided handsomely</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for his housekeeper</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:35:31.579 --> 00:35:31.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:33.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:35:33.440 --> 00:35:35.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, like any criminal,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he wanted to move on</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:35:35.918 --> 00:35:37.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>before somebody traced his whereabouts.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:35:38.387 --> 00:35:40.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He specifically requested passage</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:35:40.278 --> 00:35:44.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a vessel that was scheduled</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stop here at a Bajoran station.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:44.677 --> 00:35:47.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rather unusual request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a Cardassian war criminal.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:50.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Unless he wanted to be captured.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:35:51.434 --> 00:35:54.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Let's be clear about one thing.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:35:55.336 --> 00:35:57.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This evidence may raise</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some interesting questions.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:35:57.233 --> 00:36:00.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nevertheless, Darhe'el is going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be sent back to Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:36:01.112 --> 00:36:03.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to stand trial</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the atrocities he committed.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:36:03.510 --> 00:36:05.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, that is still to be determined.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:36:05.950 --> 00:36:07.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, then go talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:36:07.869 --> 00:36:10.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you still have any doubts,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>listen to what he has to say.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:36:11.508 --> 00:36:14.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was there. He did it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He'll tell you about it.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:36:15.187 --> 00:36:16.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:36:17.427 --> 00:36:19.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Constable, I've checked</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on Marritza's medical record.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:36:20.665 --> 00:36:21.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have we got?</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:36:22.185 --> 00:36:24.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's under treatment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Kalla-Nohra syndrome, of course,</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:36:24.584 --> 00:36:26.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and a few other minor ailments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>most relating to his age.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:36:27.184 --> 00:36:30.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all pretty standard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>really, except for one thing.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:36:30.303 --> 00:36:31.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which is?</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:36:31.742 --> 00:36:36.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Five years ago after arriving on Kora II</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he started taking massive doses</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:36:37.213 --> 00:36:40.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of dermatiraelian plastiscine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which is a dermal regenerative agent</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:36:40.460 --> 00:36:45.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>used to maintain skin resilience</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after cosmetic alteration.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:36:47.697 --> 00:36:51.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying he changed his face</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to look like Gul Darhe'el.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:36:51.656 --> 00:36:53.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It certainly appears that way.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:37:06.452 --> 00:37:07.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:37:07.931 --> 00:37:11.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was starting to get a little bored</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but seeing you again brightens my day.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:37:11.410 --> 00:37:13.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was referring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your Kalla-Nohra Syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:37:15.249 --> 00:37:16.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you like to see Dr. Bashir?</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:37:17.128 --> 00:37:18.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so that's it.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:37:18.568 --> 00:37:20.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want to see me writhing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the floor in pain.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:37:21.927 --> 00:37:24.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Cardassian would never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>put on such a deplorable display</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:37:24.526 --> 00:37:25.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in front of a Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:37:25.446 --> 00:37:26.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You just don't understand us at all.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:37:27.405 --> 00:37:29.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm beginning to understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a great deal about you.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:37:30.844 --> 00:37:31.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thing does puzzle me.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:37:32.484 --> 00:37:33.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what would that be?</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:37:34.163 --> 00:37:36.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How you contracted Kalla-Nohra Syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:36.683 --> 00:37:40.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think that the mining accident</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>affected only the Bajoran laborers</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:40.281 --> 00:37:41.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and not their Cardassian masters?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:42.201 --> 00:37:43.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That would be very nice.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:43.440 --> 00:37:46.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you're saying you were at Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when that mining accident occurred.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:46.800 --> 00:37:48.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Why are we going over this again?</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:37:49.239 --> 00:37:50.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because your own progress report</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:50.479 --> 00:37:53.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>shows you were back on Cardassia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the time of the accident.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:53.958 --> 00:37:54.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:54.837 --> 00:37:57.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Receiving your Proficient</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Service Medallion.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:57.637 --> 00:37:59.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The reports are wrong.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can show them to you.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:59.796 --> 00:38:01.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That won't be necessary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I know where I was.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:38:03.752 --> 00:38:05.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why were you taking a dermal regenerative?</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:38:05.914 --> 00:38:08.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then let me help you.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:08.634 --> 00:38:11.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Five years ago,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you first got to Kora II--</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:38:11.192 --> 00:38:12.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, that's enough!</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:12.192 --> 00:38:13.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your presence no longer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>amuses me. Get out!</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:14.151 --> 00:38:15.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did you have your face altered?</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:15.711 --> 00:38:17.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Security, get this woman out of here!</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:17.430 --> 00:38:19.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you pretending to be Gul Darhe'el?</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:19.749 --> 00:38:21.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't you ask me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something intelligent?</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:22.469 --> 00:38:25.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As for instance, how did I feel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when we were withdrawing from Bajor?</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:26.108 --> 00:38:27.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The answer is I was furious.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:38:27.747 --> 00:38:29.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The thought of leaving</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any survivors behind</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:29.626 --> 00:38:30.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>was repulsive to me.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:31.426 --> 00:38:34.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So while our useless office clerks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were packing their precious files</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:38:34.946 --> 00:38:36.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ordered my overseers</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:38:36.305 --> 00:38:38.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to begin slaughtering the laborers.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:38:39.144 --> 00:38:41.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you felt that way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about your filing clerks</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:38:41.823 --> 00:38:43.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>why did you take Marritza's name?</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:38:43.143 --> 00:38:47.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My plan was to do nothing less</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than kill every Bajoran in the camp</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:38:47.741 --> 00:38:50.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and, to this day, my one regret</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is that I was not able</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:38:50.500 --> 00:38:52.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to accomplish this honorable goal.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:53.820 --> 00:38:55.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're Marritza, aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:56.539 --> 00:38:59.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mistake me for that bug?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That whimpering nothing?</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:59.738 --> 00:39:02.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you stupid Bajoran girl.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you know who I am?</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:39:03.177 --> 00:39:05.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your nemesis. I'm your nightmare.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:39:06.536 --> 00:39:08.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the Butcher of Gallitep.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:39:08.536 --> 00:39:11.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Butcher of Gallitep</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>died six years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:39:11.535 --> 00:39:14.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're Aamin Marritza, his filing clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:39:14.414 --> 00:39:18.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not true. I am alive.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I will always be alive!</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:19.652 --> 00:39:21.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Marritza who is dead.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:21.771 --> 00:39:24.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza, who was good for nothing</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:24.908 --> 00:39:27.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but cowering under his bunk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and weeping like a woman.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:28.570 --> 00:39:33.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who, every night, covered his ears</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because he couldn't bear to hear</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:33.608 --> 00:39:37.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the screaming for mercy of the Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:37.526 --> 00:39:40.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weeping )</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:53.801 --> 00:39:55.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Covered my ears every night, but...</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:56.161 --> 00:39:58.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't bear to hear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those horrible screams.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:39:59.600 --> 00:40:02.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have no idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what it's like to be a coward...</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:40:03.998 --> 00:40:05.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To see these horrors...</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:40:06.678 --> 00:40:07.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And do nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:40:08.437 --> 00:40:10.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Marritza's dead. He deserves to be dead.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:17.915 --> 00:40:18.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:19.514 --> 00:40:20.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm letting you go.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:40:23.273 --> 00:40:24.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weakly )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Security?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:40:24.792 --> 00:40:25.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get in here.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:40:30.351 --> 00:40:33.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You didn't commit those crimes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you couldn't stop them.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:40:34.309 --> 00:40:35.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were only one man.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:35.589 --> 00:40:38.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no, don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have to be punished.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:38.469 --> 00:40:40.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We all have to be punished.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:40:40.508 --> 00:40:44.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, you have to go out and tell them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Gul Darhe'el. It's the only way.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:46.146 --> 00:40:48.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you doing this?</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:48.465 --> 00:40:51.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For Cardassia. Cardassia will only survive</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:51.184 --> 00:40:53.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if it stands in front of Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and admits the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:55.223 --> 00:40:58.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My trial will force Cardassia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to acknowledge its guilt</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:58.822 --> 00:41:00.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and we're guilty, all of us.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:41:01.581 --> 00:41:02.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My death is necessary.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:41:06.619 --> 00:41:12.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you're asking for is another murder.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Enough good people have already died.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:41:14.658 --> 00:41:16.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't help kill another.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:41:32.125 --> 00:41:35.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should be back on Kora II</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in three days.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:41:35.891 --> 00:41:37.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, there's nothing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for me to go back to.</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:37.851 --> 00:41:39.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've contacted officials there.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:39.450 --> 00:41:40.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They'll be waiting to help you.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:42.449 --> 00:41:44.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they believed that I was Gul Darhe'el</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:44.569 --> 00:41:47.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>then my trial might have helped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to bring about a new Cardassia.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:49.167 --> 00:41:51.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now you've told them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was just a file clerk.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:51.926 --> 00:41:53.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you tried to do was very honorable.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:54.925 --> 00:41:57.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Cardassia is going to change</c.bg_transparent>
